{"about_the_game":"Max Traffic is a minimalistic traffic simulator where the player controls the flow of cars by managing the traffic lights. It is a mini casual game to relax to, but also excel at, by trying to achieve the highest score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach level represents a flag, while the cars hold a minimalistic style. The sounds follow the same pattern by being abstract in their manner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 Mechanics: As simple as possible, the players just have to press on the traffic lights to change from red to green and vice versa.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 Relaxing: The game is as stressful as you want it to be, with the time also available on fast and slow. Fast however provides you with double score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 Competitive: For the hard working people out there, there is a scoring system for each level, at which everyone can excel at.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 Interesting decisions: Every level provides a different traffic management, making the players adapt to every situation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 Abilites: Every in-game day the players get an ability to help with their progression.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHope you get as many cars as you can across traffic! See you on the leaderboard!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Day At Work","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1921880/bafdaff4299c71891b29970fcba6b1b48bcd70a0.jpg"},{"name":"Traffic Maestro","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1921880/313a3ad77198e97e795b71d2634763260aef7f88.jpg"},{"name":"Master Coordinator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1921880/f8b513b1d4410d7592d725c226f8da286883b478.jpg"},{"name":"The Light Switcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1921880/9c1dc2e64426c56d3987770012c7e723c19af8cd.jpg"},{"name":"Make Them Go Boom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.